### ========================================
### 9. ENCRYPTION (AES-256-GCM + BCrypt)
### ========================================

### 11a. Encrypt plaintext → AES-256-GCM (returns Base64: Salt+Nonce+Tag+Ciphertext)
POST {{baseUrl}}/encryption/encrypt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plainText": "hola"
}

###

### 11b. Decrypt Base64 ciphertext → plaintext
### Paste the Base64 value from step 11a into EncryptedData below
@encryptedValue=SlpzS0ZHWQdpf2BJAyeBYd+o6yjiL8VX6Me9oI6OGurPOL8iZdXaFeXFxLURiPCo
POST {{baseUrl}}/encryption/decrypt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "encryptedData": "{{encryptedValue}}"
}

###

### 11c. Hash a password with BCrypt (work factor 12)
POST {{baseUrl}}/encryption/hash
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "MySecureP@ssw0rd!"
}

###

### 11d. Set password — returns BCrypt hash + Data Protection encrypted bytes (Base64)
POST {{baseUrl}}/encryption/setpassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "MySecureP@ssw0rd!"
}

###

### 11e. Decrypt password bytes (Data Protection)
### Paste the EncryptedPassword Base64 from step 11d
@encryptedPassword=REPLACE_WITH_BASE64_FROM_STEP_11D
POST {{baseUrl}}/encryption/decryptpassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "encryptedPassword": "{{encryptedPassword}}"
}

###

### 11f. Verify password against BCrypt hash
### Paste the PasswordHash from step 11d
@passwordHash=REPLACE_WITH_BCRYPT_HASH_FROM_STEP_11D
POST {{baseUrl}}/encryption/verifypassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "MySecureP@ssw0rd!",
  "passwordHash": "{{passwordHash}}"
}

###
